    <div class="my-4 text-center"><span class="math-block">\\Pr\\left(\\max_{a,b} N(a,b) \\le \\ell\\right) \\approx e^{-2^{2n}(1-\\Phi(\\ell))} . \\tag{15}</span></div>

    <p class="text-gray-300">For a permutation, λ = 1 2 and we can approximate Φ(\`) closely by [10, 19]:</p>

    <p class="text-gray-300"><span class="math-block">\\Phi(\\ell) \\approx 1 - \\frac{2\\ell}{2\\ell - 1} \\frac{e^{-\\frac{1}{2}}}{\\ell! 2^{\\ell}} .</span> (16)</p>

